headline: DTE Energy Board of Directors declares quarterly dividend
summary: (NYSE: DTE) -- The DTE Energy Board of Directors declared a $1.09 per share dividend on its common stock payable Oct. 15, 2025, to shareholders of record at the close of business Sept. 15, 2025.
